SERIES_DESC: Proportions of women and men aged 20–24 who were married or in a union before age 18
SOURCE_DETAIL: United Nations Economic and Social Council, Progress toward the Substantiable Development Goals, Report of the Secretary General – Supplementary information (E/2020/57).
